Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.77,0:22:34.29,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}向着遥远前方的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.51,0:22:36.59,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}你顺风而行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.85,0:22:44.47,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}追寻的答案不易找到
